20
00:01:19,871 --> 00:01:21,540
Hey, am I a kid?

21
00:01:22,207 --> 00:01:23,625
I set it myself

22
00:01:24,334 --> 00:01:25,419
At night, before bed

23
00:01:25,419 --> 00:01:26,712
Writing a gratitude journal too?

24
00:01:28,588 --> 00:01:29,256
Yeah

25
00:01:35,721 --> 00:01:36,972
You have a fever

26
00:01:38,557 --> 00:01:39,891
