34
00:02:12,966 --> 00:02:14,259
The things your mom tells you to do

35
00:02:14,259 --> 00:02:16,053
You've never not done them, right?

36
00:02:19,139 --> 00:02:20,015
Yeah

37
00:02:24,561 --> 00:02:26,021
If you're sick, you should go to the doctor

38
00:02:26,021 --> 00:02:27,397
Or take medicine

39
00:02:27,397 --> 00:02:28,940
Anyway, no exercise

40
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:37,657
I'll buy medicine and porridge

41
00:02:37,657 --> 00:02:40,077
You stay in bed like the dead

42
00:02:40,077 --> 00:02:40,869
Got it?

43
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:45,040
No really, I'm fine

44
00:02:57,344 --> 00:02:59,387
All the porridge shops were closed

45
00:02:59,721 --> 00:03:00,806
Does it taste okay?

46
00:03:01,598 --> 00:03:02,015
Yeah

47
00:03:02,891 --> 00:03:03,725
It's delicious

48
00:03:04,559 --> 00:03:05,519
That's good

49
00:03:10,982 --> 00:03:12,943
Seems like your fever's gone down too

50
00:03:15,403 --> 00:03:17,155
What else is set for you?

51
00:03:17,531 --> 00:03:18,990
Anything you must do?

52
00:03:18,990 --> 00:03:20,700
Or must not do?

53
00:03:23,787 --> 00:03:24,955
What else is there?

54
00:03:26,206 --> 00:03:26,957
Ah right

55
00:03:27,165 --> 00:03:28,500
You don't drink coffee either

56
00:03:28,917 --> 00:03:30,418
Is that because of your parents too?

57
00:03:30,752 --> 00:03:31,878
Yeah

58
00:03:32,212 --> 00:03:33,922
They say caffeine is bad for your body

59
00:03:33,922 --> 00:03:35,632
They absolutely won't let me drink it

60
00:03:36,758 --> 00:03:39,219
Well, caffeine isn't good for you

61
00:03:40,178 --> 00:03:41,054
And what else?

62
00:03:41,555 --> 00:03:44,724
Is there anything you've always wanted to try?

63
00:03:45,851 --> 00:03:46,768
Yeah, that's right

64
00:03:47,477 --> 00:03:48,770
There's something I want to do

65
00:03:49,271 --> 00:03:49,896
What?

66
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:52,232
Buy white sneakers

67
00:03:53,066 --> 00:03:54,025
White sneakers?

68
00:03:54,359 --> 00:03:55,026
Yeah

69
00:03:55,902 --> 00:03:58,613
They say white sneakers get dirty quickly

70
00:03:58,613 --> 00:03:59,823
So they won't let me buy them

71
00:04:00,532 --> 00:04:01,741
So until now

72
00:04:01,741 --> 00:04:03,201
