73
00:04:03,910 --> 00:04:05,370
Right...

74
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:06,288
Come to think of it

75
00:04:06,288 --> 00:04:07,956
I've never seen you wear white sneakers

76
00:04:08,915 --> 00:04:10,083
White sneakers...

77
00:04:11,001 --> 00:04:13,128
Can't you just buy them and wear them secretly?

78
00:04:14,045 --> 00:04:15,255
Well yeah

79
00:04:16,506 --> 00:04:18,216
But I can't seem to do it

80
00:04:22,804 --> 00:04:24,055
Don't worry too much

81
00:04:24,431 --> 00:04:25,432
I used to

82
00:04:25,432 --> 00:04:27,350
Not even be able to style my hair as I wanted

83
00:04:27,809 --> 00:04:28,935
But now my hair is completely

84
00:04:28,935 --> 00:04:30,478
Done my way

85
00:04:31,646 --> 00:04:33,315
Things are getting better gradually

86
00:04:34,774 --> 00:04:35,734
Are you done?

87
00:04:38,153 --> 00:04:40,155
Well, seems like your fever's gone down

88
00:04:40,155 --> 00:04:41,948
Should we go for a light walk?

89
00:04:42,991 --> 00:04:43,700
A walk?

90
00:04:49,664 --> 00:04:50,540
Wait a minute

91
00:04:57,797 --> 00:04:59,007
Wear these from now on

92
00:04:59,758 --> 00:05:00,383
Huh?

93
00:05:01,384 --> 00:05:03,762
