95
00:05:05,805 --> 00:05:06,890
They're really comfortable

96
00:05:11,603 --> 00:05:13,396
I'm okay

97
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,441
Wearing white sneakers

98
00:05:16,441 --> 00:05:17,984
Nothing's going to happen

99
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,736
If anything happens

100
00:05:19,986 --> 00:05:21,571
I'll switch back with you

101
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:31,331
Are they mine?

102
00:05:31,331 --> 00:05:32,040
Yeah

103
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:34,751
I added some syrup to yours

104
00:05:34,751 --> 00:05:36,920
Since you're drinking it, might as well make it taste good

105
00:05:37,671 --> 00:05:38,755
Thanks

106
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,134
How is it?

107
00:05:44,427 --> 00:05:45,762
The taste...

108
00:05:45,762 --> 00:05:46,972
There isn't any

109
00:05:46,972 --> 00:05:47,806
Huh?

110
00:05:48,890 --> 00:05:49,975
Is it too bitter?

111
00:05:51,559 --> 00:05:54,062
It's bitter but how should I say it?

112
00:05:55,814 --> 00:05:57,440
I think I might like it?

113
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,566
I think it's okay

114
00:05:59,109 --> 00:05:59,943
Right?

115
00:05:59,943 --> 00:06:01,069
See?

116
00:06:01,069 --> 00:06:03,238
Having caffeine occasionally is fine

117
00:06:04,948 --> 00:06:06,825
Cold? Let's go inside to drink

118
00:06:20,547 --> 00:06:21,965
What's wrong?

119
00:06:24,592 --> 00:06:26,261
I feel anxious

120
00:06:27,429 --> 00:06:28,638
Is it because I'm doing things

121
00:06:28,638 --> 00:06:31,141
My parents told me not to do?

122
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,645
Could be

123
00:06:37,939 --> 00:06:39,190
You know what?

124
00:06:41,443 --> 00:06:44,821
Fleas can jump 200 times their height

125
00:06:45,447 --> 00:06:47,407
But if you take those fleas

126
00:06:47,949 --> 00:06:50,201
And raise them in a small box

127
00:06:51,202 --> 00:06:53,330
Later when you open the box

128
00:06:53,330 --> 00:06:54,706
They can't jump out

129
00:06:55,248 --> 00:06:57,584
Because they think they can only jump that high

130
00:07:00,378 --> 00:07:01,671
So

131
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:03,548
You're like a flea

132
00:07:06,051 --> 00:07:07,635
What's that supposed to mean?

133
00:07:09,512 --> 00:07:11,222
I don't know exactly how much

134
00:07:11,222 --> 00:07:14,017
Your parents' restrictions mean to you

135
00:07:14,934 --> 00:07:15,810
But look

136
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:18,313
Nothing's happened, right?

137
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:22,192
Rather, trapped in that frame

138
00:07:22,192 --> 00:07:24,819
You might be missing out on things you like

139
00:07:27,655 --> 00:07:29,074
Actually...

140
00:07:30,408 --> 00:07:33,078
Living the way my parents set for me

141
00:07:33,078 --> 00:07:35,246
Was frustrating but comfortable

142
00:07:36,039 --> 00:07:38,917
Even if I didn't try to get recognition

143
00:07:38,917 --> 00:07:40,627
If I just followed those rules well

144
00:07:40,627 --> 00:07:42,670
They loved me

145
00:07:44,631 --> 00:07:46,674
That's why I'm anxious I guess

146
00:07:46,674 --> 00:07:49,844
Wondering if they'll love me like this too...

147
00:07:54,766 --> 00:07:56,559
If I had raised you

148
00:07:56,559 --> 00:07:59,396
I would've eaten you up from head to toe

149
00:08:04,067 --> 00:08:06,236
You're so cute I want to eat you up

150
00:08:06,986 --> 00:08:08,530
So don't try so hard

151
00:08:08,905 --> 00:08:10,365
You're beautiful as you are

152
00:08:11,157 --> 00:08:12,283
Okay?

153
00:08:14,119 --> 00:08:14,744
Yeah

154
