155
00:08:24,212 --> 00:08:26,296
You don't use hand cream?

156
00:08:28,883 --> 00:08:30,301
What's this?

157
00:08:30,301 --> 00:08:32,136
I'll put some on when we get home

158
00:08:38,977 --> 00:08:40,437
What? Is there something on my face...

159
00:09:18,975 --> 00:09:20,100
Hyena

160
00:09:23,438 --> 00:09:24,189
Huh?

161
00:09:24,856 --> 00:09:26,274
Look at me

162
00:09:44,959 --> 00:09:46,419
Why did you do that earlier?

163
00:09:51,381 --> 00:09:52,800
Well...

164
00:09:56,262 --> 00:09:57,388
I'm sorry

165
00:09:58,973 --> 00:10:00,558
What are you sorry for?

166
00:10:02,977 --> 00:10:04,354
For doing as I pleased...

167
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,981
For kissing you

168
00:10:08,858 --> 00:10:09,901
Also...

169
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:11,653
Also?

170
00:10:15,031 --> 00:10:16,658
For doing as I pleased...

171
00:10:17,534 --> 00:10:19,118
For falling for you

172
00:10:33,091 --> 00:10:34,509
I'm sorry too

173
00:10:35,176 --> 00:10:35,760
Huh?

174
00:10:36,302 --> 00:10:38,513
For falling for you on my own too
